SUMMARY:Aion 2 (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Developer/Publisher: NCSOFT\n\nAion 2 takes place 200 years aft
 er the PC game\, Aion: The Tower of Eternity.\n\nOne main feature is the a
 ppearance of dimensional cracks\, allowing players from different servers 
 to engage in large-scale PVP. Gliding and wings will no doubt be there as 
 the IP’s signature element. NCsoft even claimed Aion 2 will have features 
 which could not be realized in the PC game\, and that its vision for the g
 ame is “no longer a dream”. Such big lofty words.\n\nPerhaps the biggest d
 ifference is that there are no longer the 2 opposing factions\, Elyos and 
 Asmodians (due to the timeline). Players are free to choose to invade othe
 rs of defend. Another eye-opener is the claim of not having “class segment
 ation” in Aion 2\, with players able to wield different weapons without re
 strictions and choose their playstyle. NCsoft claims that Aion 2 will “sho
 wcase a new battle system that did not exist in the old Aion”.\n\nFinally\
 , another huge change is the removal of gliding constraints found in Aion.
  While this was not explained in detail\, NCsoft is aiming to make gliding
  part of the combat loop to create a “three dimensional battle system”. NC
 soft did not mention what engine Aion 2 is developed on\, but my guess is 
 Unreal Engine 5. Stay tuned for more updates on the game!\n\nhttps://www.i
 gdb.com/games/aion-2
END:VEVENT
