SUMMARY:Orbitals (Nintendo Switch 2)
DESCRIPTION:Developer: Shapefarm\n\nPublisher: Kepler Interactive\n\nTeam u
 p as Maki and Omura\, two inseparable explorers with a whole lot more dete
 rmination than experience. You’ll brave the perils of space in search of h
 elp for their crumbling station home\, now trapped within a supernatural c
 osmic storm.\n\nOrbitals captures the warmth and style of classic Japanese
  anime\, brought to life with hand-crafted cinematic cutscenes from Studio
  Massket\, full Japanese and English voice acting\, and an original soundt
 rack that channels the magic of the era.\n\nBuilt from the ground up for a
 symmetric 2-player co-op\, either in local split-screen or online\, Orbita
 ls rewards smart teamwork and clear communication. Use each character’s un
 ique tools to open the path forward\, overcome danger\, and meet out-of-th
 is-world creatures and characters on a bombastic adventure.\n\nhttps://www
 .igdb.com/games/orbitals--1
